{"tid":730311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新鮮we7雞招人買股實錄","createTime":"2018-07-05T09:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T10:59:25.000Z","uid":60139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96cd12bb4c4c80d474e79a193ad6f173534ef567","tid":730311,"uid":60139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:47:36.000Z","msg":"事緣上個月尾有隻we7雞add左我(add埋右), 咁我作為連登仔當然要撚下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知呢隻雞唔係叫我買點數卡，而係股票<br />\n！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢total比左3個number我<br />\n<br />\n784呢隻就咁既對話<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/173728_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F173728_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1a362688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己都幾奇怪，我無同佢講有無入市，而佢又話入唔到就唔好入，而呢隻野當日確實係升左唔少<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/173925_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F173925_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d5f0e963&s={SIZE}\" />可以睇返28號3點後既data<br />\n<br />\n另一隻就係8416<br />\n無cap圖，但係28號又係升左唔少<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/174217_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F174217_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ac754a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心諗，哇屌咁撚勁？<br />\n到左今日佢又黎料<br />\n8021<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/174317_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F174317_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=eb66bcd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知今次呢隻一個下晝跌撚左3成，今次佢就好緊張問我有無成交，又叫我影倉比佢睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/174625_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F174625_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=582e3bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我當然係鳩up喇<br />\n<br />\n去到呢到，仲有咩玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4722d357937ee7a1dbb7efc90d10614309f3f96c","tid":730311,"uid":59955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"屌 學之前有個爸打咁<br />\nsd 訊息比自己話咩價成功買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超撚真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8d979e3f047b70333942e43f2d1f9f1394c6df","tid":730311,"uid":105438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋想點？我之前都遇過，但無理到佢"},{"pid":"077c48cf5eeb27308a828fb94c1adba62d2c28c7","tid":730311,"uid":183986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"短信比自己🤪"},{"pid":"d1a9a831f4e1810e54d291f64fe69e4739483267","tid":730311,"uid":60139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4722d357937ee7a1dbb7efc90d10614309f3f96c","tid":730311,"uid":59955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"屌 學之前有個爸打咁<br />\nsd 訊息比自己話咩價成功買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超撚真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"屌但係ps唔夠勁，整唔到張圖比佢"},{"pid":"9620c2d8b5a711ac1d98b888374b6fd7cc0c9303","tid":730311,"uid":183986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"htt